=Overview=
Fetch a recipe and place it in <tt>/Files/Compile/LocalRecipes</tt>, chopping its revision number. Calls a text editor on the Recipe file afterwards.

==Usage==
   '''EditRecipe''' [ <recipe-url> | <recipe-path> | <program-name> [ program-version ] ]

==Options==
* '''<tt>-h, --help</tt>''' - Show this help.
* '''<tt>--version</tt>''' - Show program version.
* '''<tt>-v, --verbose</tt>''' - Enable verbose mode.
* '''<tt>-E, --no-edit</tt>''' - Do not edit Recipe file, just place the recipe to <tt>/Files/Compile/LocalRecipes</tt>.

==Other considerations==
* The environment variable <tt>EDITOR</tt> must be defined.


